2. Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    1. Vim/gVim text editor - http://www.vim.org
    2. War§oW free game - http://www.warsow.net

3. Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    1. Unzip all files into your $HOME/syntax/ directory.

4. Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    1. Execute while in Vim/gVim:
       :set syntax=warsow

