6. Notes and Known issues
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    I also use ftype detection for this syntax file. All files that are opened
    from my ~/.warsow directory uses this syntax.

    If you want to have the same way:
    1. Create $HOME/ftdetect/warsow.vim
    2. Insert this line:
       au BufRead,BufNewFile */.warsow/*       set filetype=warsow

